{"tid":2292540,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中大保安處處長為曾任總警司李永光，企圖拘捕中大遊行持噴漆學生！","createTime":"2020-11-19T14:26:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T16:04:58.000Z","uid":219007,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d8016424962073079e1425d4158a9a477158aa3f","tid":2292540,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T14:26:46.000Z","msg":"逾百中大學生自發今日（19 日）回校舉行「畢業遊行」，以聲援為反修例運動付出的抗爭者。遊行初期，一名畢業生企圖噴漆時遭保安阻止，在現場觀察，曾任總警司的中大保安處首長李永光，更揚言「拉佢拉佢」，惹來學生不滿。<br />\n<br />\n有律師指，市民有合理理由懷疑有人干犯可被判監一年以上罪行時，可行駛公民拘捕權；但亦有律師指出，市民行使公民拘捕權要非常小心，噴漆是否觸犯刑事毀壞未有定論，若無理拘捕侵害人身自由，可能涉及非法禁錮...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E7%95%A2%E6%A5%AD%E7%A6%AE-%E5%89%8D%E7%B8%BD%E8%AD%A6%E5%8F%B8-%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E6%9D%8E%E6%B0%B8%E5%85%89%E6%8F%9A%E8%A8%80-%E6%8B%89-%E5%99%B4%E6%BC%86%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F-%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB-%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%8F%AF%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95-%E4%BD%86%E8%A1%8C%E4%BD%BF%E4%B8%8D%E7%95%B6%E6%88%96%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E7%A6%81%E9%8C%AE/?fbclid=IwAR04NrF9jiPrP8075yatpRZUFesp6vNusGEgKtPorA8Tu7r9fT6cs9conL8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2595%25A2%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%25A6%25AE-%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%258F%25B8-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%259D%258E%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E5%2585%2589%25E6%258F%259A%25E8%25A8%2580-%25E6%258B%2589-%25E5%2599%25B4%25E6%25BC%2586%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F-%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB-%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595-%25E4%25BD%2586%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%2595%25B6%25E6%2588%2596%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E7%25A6%2581%25E9%258C%25AE%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR04NrF9jiPrP8075yatpRZUFesp6vNusGEgKtPorA8Tu7r9fT6cs9conL8&d=kK8wO%2BHHGyY98lbbYtfopZmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=d9b989ae\" data